transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Yeah, I'd like to cancel my prescription, please.

Speaker 1: Yeah, I can take a look into your prescription. What's your last name and zip code?

Speaker 2: Garrity, G-E-R-A-T-Y, 92019.

Speaker 1: Got it. I pulled up your profile here. So real quick—

Speaker 2: I do want to mention, sir, that the moment we cancel your prescription—

Speaker 1: Unfortunately, the doctor would also delete the visit, meaning you wouldn't be able to order these anymore.

Speaker 2: However, yeah, we set you up to our every six-month freeze plan.

Speaker 1: That way you can retain access to these whenever you need them down the road. Did you want to try that on?

Speaker 2: No, I'm fine. I got plenty right now.

Speaker 1: Okay, you canceled it?

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: Okay. All right. Thank you, sir.
